{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2056","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"爭取完善龜山交通路網","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2056-1.png","sequence":2056,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1BFjBZbwyS/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-04-17T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"爭取完善龜山交通路網"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"爭取完善龜山交通路網"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025/04/16 交通局質詢 🚌🚸"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔹 爭取文青國中小增設公車站與候車亭、增設行穿線及交通號誌，保障孩子上下學安全。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔹 變二道路即將開通，建議評估公車路線串聯文青國中小與合宜住宅，服務更多居民。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔹603 公車班次不足，受限於壽山路限高僅能以中巴行駛，請交通局協助業者提升車輛與人力，加開班次解決尖峰時段搭不到車的問題。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔹 評估未來郵政物流園區啟用、產專區周邊建案交屋，建議提前規劃公車路線。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔹 建議新增陽明高中直達龜山的學生專車，讓學生通勤更便利。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔹 受訓即就業有成效，交通局要加強司機訓練和留住受訓以後的公車司機。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山持續發展，交通不能落後！宗豪會繼續督促市府，完善大眾運輸路網。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2056-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2056-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"爭取完善龜山交通路網","depth":2,"text":"爭取完善龜山交通路網"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2056.md"